1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend Father Anthony M. Bozeman, SSJ, on the occasion of the twenty-fifth
3 anniversary of his ordination as a priest in the Society of St. Joseph.
4 WHEREAS, Father Anthony M. Bozeman, SSJ, is a priest in the Society of
5 St. Joseph who has dedicated his life to the service of his community; and
6 WHEREAS, Father Bozeman has guided the people of New Orleans with divine
7 inspiration and an unwavering spirit for the majority of his career; and
8 WHEREAS, Father Bozeman celebrates the twenty-fifth anniversary of his
9 ordination on Sunday, April 12, 2026.
10 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
11 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Father Anthony M. Bozeman, SSJ, on the
12 occasion of the twenty-fifth anniversary of his ordination as a priest in the Society of
13 St. Joseph; does hereby recognize his successful career as a spiritual community leader and
14 pastor; and does hereby extend sincere wishes that he remain prosperous in his endeavors
15 to serve the spiritual needs of his parishioners.
